			"id": "http://curt.micro.blog/2017/07/29/trump-is-the.html",
	      	
			"content_html": "<p>“Trump is the essence of the GOP, distilled down to its depraved and odious core. … Have no doubt: There are more horrors to come.” —<a href=\"https://www.washingtonpost.com/blogs/plum-line/wp/2017/07/28/this-is-what-you-get-when-you-elect-republicans/\">Paul Waldman</a></p>\n",
			"date_published": "2017-07-28T21:41:00-07:00",
