		},
		
		{
			"id": "http://curt.micro.blog/2017/07/29/every-vote-cast.html",
	      	
			"content_html": "<p>“Every vote cast for Donald Trump was a vote for vulgarity. His supporters got exactly what they paid for.” —<a href=\"https://www.nytimes.com/2017/07/28/opinion/trump-vulgarity-scaramucci-conservatives.html?smprod=nytcore-ipad&amp;smid=nytcore-ipad-share\">Bret Stephens</a></p>\n",
