		},
		
		{
			"id": "http://curt.micro.blog/2017/07/28/finally-mccains-actions.html",
	      	
			"content_html": "<p>Finally McCain’s actions match his rhetoric. <a href=\"https://www.nytimes.com/2017/07/27/us/politics/obamacare-partial-repeal-senate-republicans-revolt.html\">“Senate Rejects Slimmed Down Obamacare Repeal as McCain Votes No”</a></p>\n",
