		{
			"id": "http://curt.micro.blog/2017/07/28/but-can-we.html",
	      	
			"content_html": "<p>“But can we take a moment to consider the awfulness of Senator John McCain?” —<a href=\"https://www.nytimes.com/2017/07/27/opinion/columnists/trumpcare-republican-moderates.html?smprod=nytcore-ipad&amp;smid=nytcore-ipad-share\">Paul Krugman</a></p>\n",
